me" style="color:#CC7832">{@link GearmanClient::addTaskHigh()} - Add a high priority task to run in parallel</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link GearmanClient::addTaskLow()} - Add a low priority task to run in parallel</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link GearmanClient::addTaskBackground()} - Add a background task to be run in parallel</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link GearmanClient::addTaskHighBackground()} - Add a high priority background task to be run in parallel</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link GearmanClient::runTasks()} - Run a list of tasks in parallel</span></li>    </ul>   </span>  </div>   <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/class.gearmanclient.php">GearmanClient</a></div></div>
     * @return GearmanTask A GearmanTask object or false if the task could not be added*/
